25:21.186 --> 25:22.988 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
polarized.

25:22.988 --> 25:28.994 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So I do worry about some of the
limits that the movement might
have. I will just add the

25:28.994 --> 25:36.702 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Kerner Commission in 1968 put
forward a lot of these issues,
not only policing, but
unemployment

25:36.702 --> 25:42.574 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
and segregation. The black power
movement put these issues on the
table. And, unfortunately,

25:42.574 --> 25:46.712 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
