respond. So, that's a warning
for what could happen today.

25:46.712 --> 25:50.883 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: I want to ask
each one of you in just a few
seconds, how much -- what do

25:50.883 --> 25:53.552 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
