Virginia together. He is...

30:58.323 --> 31:00.358 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: It won't be the
first time she's done that.

31:00.358 --> 31:06.098 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
TAMARA KEITH: And if you're
looking at the wager lists, he's
near the top. Who knows

31:06.098 --> 31:10.268 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
if he's actually at the top of
