parlor game that we're all

31:10.268 --> 31:15.040 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
now playing, because that's what
you do this time of year, he's
near the top of the list.

31:15.040 --> 31:19.678 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Other people on that list are
Elizabeth Warren, the senator
from Massachusetts, who Hillary

31:19.678 --> 31:24.449 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
