E-word will be used, endorse
Hillary Clinton.

32:54.639 --> 32:59.277 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
TAMARA KEITH: Yes. Yes, the word
from Democratic sources with
knowledge of the negotiations

32:59.277 --> 33:02.614 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
