this is, in fact, an endorsement

33:02.614 --> 33:05.517 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
event.

33:05.517 --> 33:10.488 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Bernie Sanders and Hillary
Clinton will be campaigning
together at a rally in
Portsmouth,

33:10.488 --> 33:18.330 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
New Hampshire. This has been
weeks and weeks in the making.
One source tells me that the

33:18.330 --> 33:22.334 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
